* Primary Keys\nand Foreign Keys
** Informational only
***_ Available in Runtime 11.3 LTS+
***_ Not enforced at write time
** Primary key
***_ PRIMARY KEY constraint on table create
***_ Columns implicitly NOT NULL
***_ Supports composite (multi-column) keys
** Foreign key
***_ REFERENCES parent table
***_ Documents relationships
** Benefits
***_ Query optimizer uses for better plans
***_ Improved join strategies
***_ Can add via ALTER TABLE
@endmindmap
